## The `compose.yaml` shape

Minimum valid file â€” `services:` with one `web:` running `image: nginx:alpine`.

## The full skeleton

```yaml
name: my-app         # default = dir name
services:            # containers â€” only required block
  web:
    image: / build:      # what to run
    ports: environment: volumes:
    depends_on: healthcheck: restart:
networks: { backend: {} }    # default auto-created
volumes:  { pgdata:  {} }    # like docker volume create
```

## The mental model

Each service = a **`docker run` in YAML**: `-p`â†’`ports`, `-e`â†’`environment`, `-v`â†’`volumes`. Top-level `networks:` / `volumes:` = shared resources referenced by name.
